::  ++  cut                                               ::< mass delete
::    ::>  pos: first position
::    ::>  num: characters to delete
::    ::
::    |=  {pos/@ud num/@ud}
::    ^-  sole-edit
::    :-  %mor
::    |-  ^-  (list sole-edit)
::    ?:  =(0 num)  ~
