::  ::
::  ++  rep                                               ::< mass replace
::    ::>  combined cut and cat
::    ::>
::    ::>  pos: position
::    ::>  num: characters to delete
::    ::>  txt: characters to replace them with
::    ::
::    |=  {{pos/@ud num/@ud} txt/(list @c)}
::    ^-  sole-edit
::    :~  %mor
::        (cut pos num)
::        (cat pos txt)
